
OBJECTIVE(2)               silmul_efun               OBJECTIVE(2)

名稱
     objective - 根據性別(gender)傳回適當的稱謂(pronoun)

語法
     string objective(string gender);

描述
     Provides an appropriate object pronoun based  on  gender  as
     follows:

     "male"    -> "him" "female"   ->  "her"  "neuter"   ->  "it"
     (other)   -> "hir"

相關命令
     /adm/simul_efun/pronouns.c

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/5/93
     wade@future 4/8/1996 翻譯

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

